Parc Manovo Gounda, St. Floris. Yagounda creek 6 km E of confluence with Koumbala River. Setaria sphacelata wet meadow with Ascolepis protea, Hyparrhenia nyassae, Otomeria elatior. Soil: enriched sandy loam on sandstone. Dense caespitose perennial.
